    ALSA: hda - Remove superfluous pcm NULL check
    
    The variable pcm can be never NULL since it was rewritten with
    list_for_each_entry().
    
    Suggested-by: Markus Osterhoff <linux-kernel@k-raum.org>
    Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

